Package: timbow
Type: Package
Title: Generate Rainbow HEX Colors with a Perceptual Luminosity Gradient
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Timothy R. Koscik [aut, cre, cph]
Maintainer: Timothy Koscik <timkoscik@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Description: Uses HSLuv color specifications to generate color gradients that begin with a desired hue and vary in colorfulness and luminosity along the desired gradient. Hence, rainbows translate more directly to grayscale gradients for non-color printing (in theory).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
